<div class="title">Weird Visual Disturbance</div>
<div class="substance">B. caapi, Syrian Rue, & Psychoactive Amanita spp.</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Ripper&Exact=1">Ripper</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Ripper. "Weird Visual Disturbance: An Experience with B. caapi, Syrian Rue, & Psychoactive Amanita spp. (exp41049)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 28, 2005. erowid.org/exp/41049</div>

